page1.title: About Me
page1.content: About . Peter Yang earned a Ph.D in Computer Cryptology a decade ago. Peter has been in IT industry for more than 15 years. His early career focused on designing threshold encryption algorithms and teaching Computer Cryptology in university. Since 2015, he is mainly focused on Python and its ecosystem. . Contact . Peter can be contacted by sending email to pyoung1683@gmail.com .
